SQL:select  `user`.`UserId` , `user`.`NickName` from `user`   where `user`.`UserID` ='4'
SQL:select  `image`.`ImageId` , `image`.`imgurl`, `image`.`Description`,`user`.*  from `image`  INNER JOIN  `user` ON  `image`.`author` =  `user`.`UserId`  where `image`.`GroupID` ='11'
SQL:select *,`user`.*  from `comments`  INNER JOIN  `user` ON  `comments`.`UserId` =  `user`.`UserId`  where `comments`.`ImgGroupId` ='11'
SQL:select *,`image`.`ImageId`  from  `image` INNER JOIN  `user` ON  `image`.`author` =  `user`.`UserId`  ORDER BY ImageId desc limit 0,30
SQL:select `user`.`NickName` ,`user`.`UserId`  from  `user`  limit 0,30
SQL:select *,`imagegroup`.`ImagegroupId`  from  `imagegroup`  ORDER BY likes DESC limit 0,5

SQL:select  `imagegroup`.`ImagegroupId` , `imagegroup`.`GroupName`, `imagegroup`.`Description`, `imagegroup`.`author` from `imagegroup`   where `imagegroup`.`ImagegroupID` ='35'
SQL:select  `user`.`UserId` , `user`.`NickName` from `user`   where `user`.`UserID` ='23'
